--><!-- 
daba siddham : At the end I follow the reading suggested by Sanyal's editor and adopted by Agrawala. Sanyal himself read bhavanā(tha)#1#, while Sircar read nothing after bhava. Segmentation is arbitrary. 
--><!-- 
daba siddham : I think an initial ī is rare enough to deserve comment. Initial i in this inscription looks like :| while this ī character is :|° (single dot, not circle, to the right of the bar). 
--><lb 
